The paper deals with the sorting problem and proposes a new variant of QuickMergesort that combines Quicksort with Mergesort to achieve worst-case efficiency. This falls under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and algorithm analysis and complexity (cs.AL). The paper also presents experimental results and theoretical analysis, which could fall under the categories of data management (cs.DM), computational complexity (cs.CC), and information theory (cs.IT).
